<topic template="Default" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd">
  <title translate="true">Preparing Queries</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword translate="true">Preparing Queries</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Preparing Queries</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">In addition to preparing SQL statements for later execution, you can also prepare </text><text styleclass="Class Name" translate="true">SELECT</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> queries. For example:</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><text styleclass="Code Example" translate="true">ps := c prepare: &apos;select * from Customers where CompanyName &gt;= ?&apos;.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><text styleclass="Code Example" translate="true">ps paramCols: ((c columns: &apos;Customers&apos;) select: [:col | col name=&apos;CompanyName&apos;]).</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Then execute later and retrieve the results with a #</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">results</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> message.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><text styleclass="Code Example" translate="true">ps values: #(&apos;G&apos;).</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><text styleclass="Code Example" translate="true">ps exec.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><text styleclass="Code Example" translate="true">ps results. &quot;Inspect it&quot;</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">and:</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><text styleclass="Code Example" translate="true">ps values: #(&apos;Rattlesnake&apos;).</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><text styleclass="Code Example" translate="true">ps exec.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Code Example"><text styleclass="Code Example" translate="true">ps results. &quot;Inspect it&quot;</text></para>
  </body>
</topic>
